[04/06/2017 00:44:26] <font color="#ffff00">se convierten poco a poco</font>
[04/06/2017 00:44:28] <font color="#ffff00">en elementos incontrolables</font>
[04/06/2017 00:44:31] <font color="#ffff00">de la cultura popular</font>
