[04/06/2017 14:00:14] <font color="#00ffff">La sangre se entristece</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:14] <font color="#00ffff">de batirse sola.</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:17] <font color="#00ffff">Los ojos vuelven tristes</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:17] <font color="#00ffff">de mal conocimiento.</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:20] <font color="#00ffff">Cada ciudad, dormida,</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:20] <font color="#00ffff">despierta loca,</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:22] <font color="#00ffff">exhala un silencio de cárcel,</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:23] <font color="#00ffff">de sueño que arde y llueve</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:26] <font color="#00ffff">como un élitro ronco</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:26] <font color="#00ffff">de no poder ser ala.</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:29] <font color="#00ffff">El hombre yace.</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:29] <font color="#00ffff">El cielo se eleva.</font>
[04/06/2017 14:00:30] <font color="#00ffff">El aire mueve".</font>
