[04/06/2017 22:18:40] <font color="#ffffff">en la carretera.</font>
[04/06/2017 22:18:43] <font color="#ffff00">Ernie Braddock</font>
[04/06/2017 22:18:43] <font color="#ffff00">se beneficiará económicamente</font>
